org.ogf.saga.attributes
Interface Attributes

All Known Subinterfaces:
AsyncAttributes<T>, Context, Job, JobDescription, JobSelf, LogicalDirectory, LogicalFile, Metric, Stream
public interface Attributes

Provides a uniform paradigm to set and query parameters and properties of SAGA objects. Attributes map a key to a value.
